# pdfminer.six Insecure Deserialization (GHSA-f83h-ghpp-7wcc)
# ----------------------------------------------------------
# Status: No upstream fix available (as of December 2025)
# Severity: HIGH (CVSS 7.8) - Local privilege escalation
#
# Risk Assessment:
# - Requires local access + write permissions to CMap cache
# - Container runs as non-root user with read-only CMap dirs
# - PDF files are only from authenticated users
# - Attack surface is significantly reduced in containerized deployment
#
# Decision: Accept risk with monitoring for upstream fix
# Review Date: 2025-12-16
# Documented: docs/ci-workflow-issues-handoff.md (Issue 6)
GHSA-f83h-ghpp-7wcc
